<plot>Harlem's mean streets. As the soundtrack plays "Watch Ya Back," a young man runs through the streets, glancing back, afraid. In a flashback that same day, we see him walk past three young toughs who watch him enter a convenience store. They stare in after him. When he leaves, they give chase and he runs for his life. Why are they chasing him? What's he done? What waits at the end? Whoa.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?655496</url></doc>
